  <brief_title>Four-week Study of the Safety and Efficacy of NLS-2 (Mazindol Extended Release) in the Treatment of Narcolepsy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Four-week, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Randomized, Multicenter, Parallel-group Study of the Safety and Efficacy of NLS-2 (Mazindol Extended Release) in Adults for the Treatment of Narcolepsy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
