    <is_fda_regulated_device>No</is_fda_regulated_device>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a double-blind, randomized, placebo-controlled, multicenter trial of NLS-2 in adult&#xD;
      patients with narcolepsy. The study will enroll approximately 60 patients and eligible&#xD;
      patients will be treated to receive either NLS-2 or placebo for 4-weeks.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
